  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 350 \u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The price of wheat flour is 350 rupees?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The All Sri Lanka Bakery Owners Association said that the price of one kilogram of wheat flour in the market has increased to 350 rupees.",
        "The association said that only 25% of the daily demand from the two major wheat flour importers is being released to the market.",
        "Traders bringing wheat flour to Sri Lanka have raised the price of wheat flour to Rs 350 as India has temporarily banned exports.(R)"
      ],
